Privacy Policy
Basu Apps built the Wane Loulou Icon Pack app as a commercial application. Wane Loulou Icon Pack is an icon pack customization application for Android devices that allows users to apply custom icons and wallpapers to their device launcher. This SERVICE is provided by Basu Apps and is intended for use as is.

This page is used to inform visitors regarding our policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information if anyone decided to use our Service.

If you choose to use our Service, then you agree to the collection and use of information in relation to this policy. The Personal Information that we collect is used for providing and improving the Service. We will not use or share your information with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy.

The terms used in this Privacy Policy have the same meanings as in our Terms and Conditions, which is accessible at Wane Loulou Icon Pack unless otherwise defined in this Privacy Policy.

Information Collection and Use

For a better experience while using our Service, we may collect certain information to provide and improve the Service. The types of information collected include:

Device Information: We may collect device information such as device model, operating system version, and unique device identifiers for the purpose of license verification and app functionality.
App Usage Data: Information about how you use the app, including which icons are applied and which features are used, to improve user experience.
Purchase Information: If you make in-app purchases, we collect payment information through Google Play Billing to process transactions.
We do not collect personal information such as your name, email address, or phone number unless you voluntarily provide it to us.

